                    <div class=\"tbasic\">\n                                <div class=\"tname\">颜立新</div>\n                                <div class=\"tposition\">博士、副教授</div>\n                                <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"tcontent\">\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>清华大学核技术研究所加速器教研室</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>邮  箱: yanlx@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                                  <p>Tel: 86-10-62799243</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>Fax: 86-10-62799243</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                   <p></p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                        </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu\">  \n                     \n       <li class=\"on\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教育背景</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">工作经历</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教学工作</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究领域</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究概况</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术成果</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">奖励与荣誉</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n    </ul> \n    \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-on\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2001.08-2006.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，获得核技术及应用专业博士学位</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>1997.08-2001.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，获得核工程与技术专业学士学位</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br></span></p>\n</div></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2012.12-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，副研究员、副教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2008.07-2012.11<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，助理研究员</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2006.07-2008.06<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系，博士后</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>讲授《射线源导论》本科生课程；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>讲授《高亮度电子束物理及应用》研究生课程；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">● 合作</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">讲授《</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">工程应用中的物理奥妙与物理探索中的工程实践》</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">本科生实验课程；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify;\">● 合作</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-wrap: wrap;\">讲授《</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">专业基础实验</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">》本科生实验课程；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>指导研究生人数情况：毕业11人（9博+2硕），在读9人（8博+硕）。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>新型太赫兹辐射源技术及其应用研究；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>先进光学增益腔技术及应用研究；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>激光技术及其在先进光源领域的应用研究；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>高亮度电子源产生、诊断与应用研究；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>逆康普顿散射X射线及伽马射线源研究等。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2024年—2029年，北京市高校卓越青年科学家计划，项目负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2022年—2027年，高功率激光电子束调制关键技术，科技部重点研发计划，课题负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2020年—2021年，***研究，创新特区，项目负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2019年—2023年，新型高聚束因子可调太赫兹结构电子束脉冲序列及其辐射研究，国家自然科学基金重点，项目负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2017年—2018年，强场THz与物质相互作用研究，创新特区，项目负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2015年—2018年，基于非线性纵向空间电荷振荡的可调窄带太赫兹辐射物理及技术问题研究，国家自然科学基金，项目负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2013年—2016年，***机理研究，国家863创新，项目负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2012年—2015年，***技术研究，教育部支撑项目，项目负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2014年—2017年，结合扫描隧道显微技术与太赫兹光谱学研究新奇量子物质，科技部重大仪器专项任务，课题负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2010年—2012年，基于光阴极微波电子枪的ps间隔超短电子束团序列的产生研究，国家自然科学基金，项目负责人；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2009年—2016年，***THz源研究，国家863计划，项目负责人。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. ZY Liu, XJ Deng, T Li, LX Yan*, Instantaneous and retarded interactions in coherent radiation, Phys. Rev. Lett. 133, 165001(2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. XY Lu, et al, Stable 500 kW average power of infrared light in a finesse 35 000 enhancement cavity, Appl. Phys. Lett. 124(25),251105(2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. XY Lu, et al, 710 kW stable average power in a 45 000 finesse two-mirror optical cavity, Opt. Lett. 49(23), 6884(2024)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4. YF Liang, ZY Liu, QL Tian, T Li, XC Lin, LX Yan*, YC Du, RK Li, JR Shi, C Cheng, WH Huang, CX Tang, Widely tunable electron bunch trains for the generation of high-power narrowband 1–10 THz radiation, Nature Photonics 17, 259–263 (2023)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">5. YF Liang, S Antipov, QL Tian, LX Yan*, et al, Generation of a chirp-controlled THz pulse by a tapered corrugated wakefield structure, Phys. Rev. Applied 19, 054085(2023)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">6. LX Yan*, ZY Liu, Efficient free electron laser, Nature Photonics 16, 404-405(2022)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">7. HQ Feng, Z Zhou, YP Wu*, ZF Gao, YF Liang, NS Huang, LX Yan*, et al, Generation of tunable 10-mJ-level THz pulses through nonlinear plasma wakefield modulation, Phys. Rev. Applied 15, 044032(2021)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">8. QL Tian, HX Xu, Y Wang, YF Liang, YM Tan, XN Ning, LX Yan*, et al, Efficient generation of a high-field THz pulse train in bulk LN crystals by optical rectification, Opt. Express 29(6), 9624-9634(2021)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">9. HX Xu, LX Yan, YC Du, WH Huang*,QL Tian, RK Li, YF Liang, SH Gu, JR Shi, CX Tang, Cascaded high-gradient THz-driven acceleration of relativistic electron beams, Nature Photonics 15, 426-430(2021)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">10. XJ Deng, A Chao, J Feikes*, A Hoehl, WH Huang, R Klein, A Kruschinski, J Li, A Matveenko, Y Petenev, M Ries, CX Tang*, LX Yan, Experimental demonstration of the mechanism of SSMB, Nature 590, 576-579(2021)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">11. YF Liang, YC Du, XL Su, D Wang, LX Yan*, et al, Observation of coherent Smith-Purcell and transition radiation driven by single bunch and micro-bunched electron beams, Appl. Phys. Lett. 112 (5), 053501(2018)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">12. YF Liang, YC Du, D Wang, LX Yan*, et al, Selective excitation and control of coherent THz Smith-Purcell radiation by high-intensity period-tunable train of electron micro-bunches, Appl. Phys. Lett. 113, 171104(2018)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">13. LR Zhao, Z Wang, C Lu, R Wang, C Hu, P Wang, J Qi, T Jiang, SG Liu, ZR Ma, FF Qi, PF Zhu, Y Cheng, ZW Shi, YC Shi, W Song, XX Zhu, JR Shi, YX Wang, LX Yan, et al, THz Streaking of Few-fs Relativistic Electron Beams, Phys. Rev. X 8(2), 021061(2018)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">14. D Wang*, XL Su, LX Yan*, et al, Phase control with two-beam interferometry method in a terahertz dielectric wakefield accelerator, Appl. Phys. Lett. 111 (17), 174102(2017)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">15. Zhang Z, Yan LX, et al, Tunable High-Intensity Electron Bunch Train Production Based on Nonlinear Longitudinal Space Charge Oscillation, Phys. Rev. Lett. 116(18), 184801(2016)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">16. FC Fu, R Wang, PF Zhu, LR Zhao, T Jiang, C Lu, SG Liu, LB Shi, LX Yan, et al, Demonstration of Nonlinear-Energy-Spread Compensation in Relativistic Electron Bunches with Corrugated Structures, Phys. Rev. Lett. 114 (11), 114801(2015)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">17. Yan LX, et al, Passive energy jitter reduction in the cascaded third harmonic generation process, Las. Phys. Lett. 11, 075403(2014)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">18. XL Xu, JF Hua, F Li, CJ Zhang, LX Yan, et al, Phase-Space Dynamics of Ionization Injection in Plasma-Based Accelerators, Phys. Rev. Lett. 112 (3), 035003(2014)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">19. F Li, JF Hua, XL Xu, CJ Zhang, LX Yan, et al, Generating High-Brightness Electron Beams via Ionization Injection by Transverse Colliding Lasers in a Plasma-Wakefield Accelerator, Phys. Rev. Lett. 111 (1), 015003(2013)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">20. Chen HB, Du YC, Gai W, Grudiev A, Hua JF, Huang WH, Power JG,Wisniewski EE, Wuensch W, Tang CX, Yan LX, et al., Surface Emission Studies in a High Field RF Gun based on Measurements of Field Emission and Schottky Enabled Photoemission, Phys. Rev. Lett. 109, 204802 (2012)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span><br></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2023年，中国光学十大进展提名奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2021年，中国光学十大影响力事件提名奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2021年，中国光学十大进展提名奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2020年，北京市科技进步一等奖，</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2009年，清华大学优秀班/级主任一等奖</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2010年，清华大学优秀军工定向生导师</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div class=\"links-box\">\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:20px;\"></div>\n            <div class=\"model-title\">\n                <div class=\"model\">常用链接</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"model-block\"></div>\n            <ul>\n      <a href=\"https://ww